 covers the K8s/AgentCube Provider functionality in the AgentCube CLI, enabling deployment to either standard Kubernetes (Deployment + Service) or AgentCube's custom AgentRuntime CR.\\n\\n## Base Specifications\\n\\n- **AR**: AR-026\\n- **Module**: `cmd/cli`\\n- **Language**: Python\\n- **Size**: M\\n- **Base Specs**: cli-toolkit/spec.md\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Background\\n\\nThe AgentCube CLI supports deploying agents to two target providers:\\n1. **agentcube**: Uses AgentRuntime CR (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`) for deployment\\n2. **k8s**: Uses standard Kubernetes Deployment + NodePort Service\\n\\nThis delta focuses on the provider-specific publish, invoke, and status workflows.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: `publish` command — Provider selection\\n\\nThe system SHALL support `--provider` option to select deployment target.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Publish with agentcube provider (default)\\n- **GIVEN** the user runs `publish` with `--provider agentcube` (or default)\\n- **WHEN** metadata contains `router_url` and `workload_manager_url`\\n- **THEN** the system SHALL deploy via `AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime`\\n\\n#### Scenario: Publish with k8s provider\\n- **GIVEN** the user runs `publish --provider k8s`\\n- **WHEN** Kubernetes client initializes successfully\\n- **THEN** the system SHALL deploy via `KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent` with NodePort Service\\n\\n#### Scenario: Publish with k8s provider — NodePort specification\\n- **GIVEN** the user runs `publish --provider k8s --node-port 30080`\\n- **WHEN** the deployment is created\\n- **THEN** the Service SH...\n  Line 22: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775866744762,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28618f847ffeO2FZgDArMKgtuE\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79e80813001B7H1ovwZeQYO7e\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79e7fb2a001e2CIEwfLHJ0IB2\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28618f847ffeO2FZgDArMKgtuE\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Done. I've written the delta-spec.md for AR-026 at `changes/AR-026/delta-spec.md` with GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios covering:\\n\\n- **publish** command: provider selection, NodePort/replicas/namespace options, prerequisites validation\\n- **Kubernetes provider**: Deployment + NodePort Service creation, readiness waiting, deletion\\n- **AgentCube provider**: AgentRuntime CR deployment with required fields\\n- **invoke** command: provider-based routing, session header injection\\n- **status** command: provider-specific status retrieval\\n- **Error handling**: K8s client unavailability, deployment timeout\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775866744760,\"end\":1775866744760}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z_logs/AR-021_ST-3.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775866682398,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28618f4c1ffehZCIrdTuY0QXWP\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79e7175f001vJ2Q3wj32FyVVt\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79e70c410019j2aBfHKSdUyGt\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28618f4c1ffehZCIrdTuY0QXWP\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_9482214a878f4e77a6d8e68f\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/.sdd_prompt.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/.sdd_prompt.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: Write design.md with technical implementation details for the agentcube project:\\n2: \\n3: AR: AR-021 — CLI build 命令\\n4: Module: cmd/cli\\n5: Language: Python\\n6: Size: M\\n7: \\n8: Specs:\\n9: --- cli-toolkit/design.md ---\\n10: # AgentCube CLI (cli-toolkit) — Design\\n11: \\n12: Source root: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/cmd/cli/`.\\n13: \\n14: ## Package layout (every module path and role)\\n15: \\n16: | Path | Role |\\n17: |------|------|\\n18: | `pyproject.toml` | Project metadata, dependencies, console script mapping |\\n19: | `agentcube/__init__.py` | Package version `__version__`, expor